name: Investor's Edge DAO
description: A community driven ecosystem enabling people to invest in assets & businesses, dually owning equity in the DAOs assets & assisting entrepreneurs in gaining access to easy funding (for both startups and business expansion). We promote a symbiotic relationship being that the community owns a piece of EVERY INVESTMENT funded by the DAO, in turn creating a vested interest in the success of both business & community
payDisclosure: you will receive tokens that will give you voting rights, enabling you to make decisions regarding the DAOs funds.
